	                           </div>
                           " style="cursor:pointer;"><i class="bi bi-person-plus me-3 fs-5"></i>회원가입</a>
	                        <a class="nav-link my-3 ms-2 link-dark" href="/contents"><i class="bi bi-card-text fs-5 me-3"></i>컨텐츠</a>
